We have to make sacrifices.

354
00:22:02,863 --> 00:22:05,113
These are the ones who do not eat the eye. They do not hold the tongue.

355
00:22:06,113 --> 00:22:07,279
- These are..
- Oh.?

356
00:22:07,279 --> 00:22:08,696
How far is it from here to you?

357
00:22:09,071 --> 00:22:12,154
That is, on foot.
That would take a day to reach

358
