Come on. Let's go and pray.

371
00:22:35,321 --> 00:22:36,446
- Huh?
- Hmm.

372
00:22:37,446 --> 00:22:39,238
We are going out across the border for the first time.

373
00:22:39,238 --> 00:22:40,488
My dear.

374
00:22:40,488 --> 00:22:42,738
Swami Panjurli.

375
