From here, your path is yours, mine is mine.

512
00:30:21,058 --> 00:30:23,058
Don't tell anyone that I brought you here .

513
00:30:23,058 --> 00:30:24,975
No, that's all I'll say if anyone asks.

514
00:30:25,016 --> 00:30:26,016
That!

515
00:30:26,604 --> 00:30:28,812
I wonder if I'll be at the butcher shop tomorrow.

516
00:30:32,558 --> 00:30:33,725
Shh! Shh!

517
00:30:35,433 --> 00:30:36,891
Oh! Good!

518
